M||conf|[02-general.md]
M||tx|---
M|Rout|it|Use App Router — no Pages Router patterns
M|Rout|it|Keep `page.tsx` files thin — logic goes in cp or server actions
M|Rout|it|Use `loading.tsx` and `er.tsx` at every rt level
M|Serv|it|Default to Server cp — only use `"use client"` when you need interactivity
M|Serv|it|Never leak ap keys or secrets to client cp
M|Serv|it|All ap calls go through server-side rt handlers — never call external APIs from client
M|Data|it|Use `fetch()` w/ `cache` options in Server cp
M|Data|it|Use rc Query or SWR for client-side data that changes
M|Data|it|Never fetch in `useEffect` unless unavoidable
M|perf|it|Use `nx/im` for all images — never plain `<img>`
M|perf|it|Use `nx/font` for custom fonts
M|perf|it|Lazy-load heavy cp w/ `dynamic()`
M|API |it|All ap rt in `app/ap/[rt]/rt.ts`
M|API |it|Always validate request body w/ Zod
M|API |it|Return consistent `{ data, er }` shape
M|sb|it|Use server-side sb client for mutations
M|sb|it|Use RLS — never bypass row-level sec
M|sb|it|All DB queries parameterized — no string interpolation